text: Meißendorf is a village and Ortschaft (municipal division) of the municipality of Winsen an der Aller in Celle in northern Germany.Hauptsatzung der Gemeinde Winsen (Aller) , December 2020. It is northwest of Winsen an der Aller. It comes from its name from the river Meiße which flows through the village. == Literature == * Judaslohn, crime novel by Andree Hesse, , (set in Eichendorf (= Meißendorf) and the nearby military training area) ==References== Category:Villages in Lower Saxony Category:Lüneburg Heath Category:Winsen an der Aller
